        {
            "title": "委內瑞拉石油出口在馬杜羅倒台後飆升 中國購買量歸零",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 委內瑞拉原油出口連續第3個月上升，4月份超過每日100萬桶，凸顯出在強人尼古拉斯·馬杜羅下台尚不到6個月，原油出口就迅速反彈。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自美國今年早些時候開始控制該國石油銷售以來，出口量一直在快速恢復。根據彭博追蹤的航運報告和油輪動態，4月份出口飆升至每日116萬桶，創下7年高點，較去年年底的水平翻了一番。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著美國制裁放鬆，使得通過管道運輸黏稠原油所必需的稀釋劑恢復穩定進口，產量也得以提升，3月份產量接近每日100萬桶，為2019年以來最高。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f5fe8681-25ae-32eb-9a60-c52c4451be39-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">印度煉油商是委內瑞拉石油的最大買家，填補了中國留下的空白。自馬杜羅倒台以來，中國一直沒有購買任何委內瑞拉原油。美國燃料生產商增加了進口量，4月份進口量接近每日40.7萬桶，較前一個月高出16%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Venezuela Oil Exports Hit 1 Million B/d in Post-Maduro Era</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A7%94%E5%85%A7%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%9C%A8%E9%A6%AC%E6%9D%9C%E7%BE%85%E5%80%92%E5%8F%B0%E5%BE%8C%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%87-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B3%BC%E8%B2%B7%E9%87%8F%E6%AD%B8%E9%9B%B6-190312558.html",
